    <!--
         This allows the menu to extend beyond the edge of the screen for proper height
         calculations. Without this, the menu's height will be clipped to the edges of the screen,
         and we can't readjust the placement/size properly. We need enough room for the largest
         possible menu height minus half of the screen height because the items that allow the least
         space for the menu are those in the vertical center. So these are the cases where the menu
         has the potential to extend beyond the screen edge the greatest amount.
    -->
